# Benvenuti

Since 1987: one dish[sidenote]The health inspector asked why. We asked him, gently, to
leave.[/sidenote], done right. Our founder, Giuseppe "The Hat" Borsalino, believed a
restaurant should do exactly *one thing* perfectly. He also believed in hats. Only one of
these beliefs made it onto the menu.

[marquee]FRESH SPAGHETTI DAILY · THE ONLY THING WE HAVE · YOU KNOW WHY YOU'RE HERE ·[/marquee]

[blink]**TONIGHT'S SPECIAL: spaghetti.**[/blink]

No reservations. No substitutions. No regrets.

